{"id":49762,"date":"2024-08-20T12:46:00","date_gmt":"2024-08-20T07:16:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=49762"},"modified":"2024-11-13T09:55:45","modified_gmt":"2024-11-13T04:25:45","slug":"simple-bedroom-interior-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/simple-bedroom-interior-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"10 Simple Bedroom Interior Design Ideas Perfect for Your Indian Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Try these simple bedroom interior designs to take your aesthetic vibe up a notch<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The key to achieving a simple bedroom interior design is to play with selective elements and let them shine. Your bedroom is a space that should ooze of cosy comfort and convenience. Although evolving trends can make it difficult to choose between the stunning colours, textures, and accents available today, it is important to let your bedroom be a haven of tranquillity. It should be a room that is not high maintenance or a space that eats up your time and energy cleaning it. If you have a busy schedule but want to keep things chic yet affordable, these 10 simple bedroom design ideas can help you get inspired.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simple Bedroom Design With Natural Light&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In a world where everyone is trying to reduce their carbon footprint, having ample natural light can help save more units on our electricity bill. Besides saving on money, natural light seeping through this stylish balcony window gate replenishes Vitamin D deficiency and amplifies the ambience of this simple <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom design<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122948\/simple-bedroom-interior-design-with-natural-light.jpg\" alt=\"Simple bedroom interior design which has ample natural light to enhance the ambience\" class=\"wp-image-49774\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122948\/simple-bedroom-interior-design-with-natural-light.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122948\/simple-bedroom-interior-design-with-natural-light-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122948\/simple-bedroom-interior-design-with-natural-light-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122948\/simple-bedroom-interior-design-with-natural-light-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Natural light creates the illusion of a more spacious room <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pops of Colour for a Simple Bedroom Interior<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Colour has the power to transform even the most simple <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom interiors<\/a>. If you love your neutrals, try adding one solid colour and balancing it throughout the room. Using green with natural materials like a jute pouffe and rattan planter creates a symphony of cohesiveness throughout the room.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122930\/simple-bedroom-design-with-pop-of-colours.jpg\" alt=\"Simple bedroom interior design which has pops of colour\" class=\"wp-image-49772\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122930\/simple-bedroom-design-with-pop-of-colours.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122930\/simple-bedroom-design-with-pop-of-colours-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122930\/simple-bedroom-design-with-pop-of-colours-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122930\/simple-bedroom-design-with-pop-of-colours-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Create a focal point using just one piece of furniture<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simple Indian Bedroom Interior Design with Laminate Floors<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you love <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/everything-about-hardwood-flooring\/\">hardwood floors<\/a> but find it a hassle to keep them clean with your busy lifestyle? The best alternative to keeping your bedroom interiors cheap and low-maintenance is by using <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/laminate-wood-flooring-designs\/\">laminate flooring<\/a>.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122938\/simple-indian-bedroom-interior-design.jpg\" alt=\"Simple bedroom interior design in indian style with laminate flooring\" class=\"wp-image-49773\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122938\/simple-indian-bedroom-interior-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122938\/simple-indian-bedroom-interior-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122938\/simple-indian-bedroom-interior-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122938\/simple-indian-bedroom-interior-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Using brown in the room adds visual interest to the space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Monochromatic Simple Bedroom Design Ideas&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>What\u2019s not to love about a classic black-and-white <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/contemporary-bedroom-designs\/\">contemporary bedroom design<\/a>? A wall-to-wall carpeted floor might not be the easiest to clean, but why not if you have the help? Clean lines and modern lighting elevate this small bedroom into an abode of peace.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122911\/monochromatic-simple-bedroom-design-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Simple bedroom interior design in monochromatic style\n\" class=\"wp-image-49770\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122911\/monochromatic-simple-bedroom-design-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122911\/monochromatic-simple-bedroom-design-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122911\/monochromatic-simple-bedroom-design-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122911\/monochromatic-simple-bedroom-design-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Panelled walls add class to the simple bedroom design \n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simple Small Bedroom Interior Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Middle-class Indian homes with large families and small homes often need to spark up creative designs to accommodate everyone comfortably. This pull-out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sofa-cum-bed-designs\/\">sofa cum bed<\/a> is an excellent idea to install in a study room that serves a dual purpose. Have guests? Use the room as a living room during the day and a bedroom at night.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122921\/simple-small-bedroom-interior-design.jpg\" alt=\"Simple interior design of a small bedroom which includes storage cabinets on the wall\" class=\"wp-image-49771\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122921\/simple-small-bedroom-interior-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122921\/simple-small-bedroom-interior-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122921\/simple-small-bedroom-interior-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122921\/simple-small-bedroom-interior-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Storage cabinets built on the wall for small homes \n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simple Indian Bedroom Interior Design Ideas&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to divert from an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/white-bedrooms\/\">all-white bedroom vibe<\/a>, this design has a colour palette with a striking yet serene vibe. A warm yellow textured wall against a teal bed and wood accents add style to the room. Clusters of small paintings, a mirror, and a vibrant floor rug bring personalised charm to the bedroom.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122838\/simple-indian-bedroom-interior-design-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Simple indian bedroom interior design with green plants for positive vibes\n\" class=\"wp-image-49766\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122838\/simple-indian-bedroom-interior-design-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122838\/simple-indian-bedroom-interior-design-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122838\/simple-indian-bedroom-interior-design-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122838\/simple-indian-bedroom-interior-design-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Adding green plants fills the space with positive vibes <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Looking for aesthetic bedroom interiors that spark joy\" src=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/looking-for-aesthetic-bedroom-interiors-that-spark-joy.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simple Bedroom Interior Design for Storage Maximisation&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Your small <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/country-style-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">country-side bedroom<\/a> is design goals, but is it storage efficient? This design brings modern elements with a twist for small Indian homes. The stylish bed features easy-to-pull-out drawers that store your everyday linens. A cabinet and small cupboard matching the bed blend with the room seamlessly while using empty corner space.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/20122828\/simple-bedroom-interior-design-for-storage-maximisation.jpg\"